				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2019 15:50:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>More Power</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5054156</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The Hebrew is Shema Yisrael, which is basically the Jewish equivalent to the Lord’s Prayer in terms of it being the major prayer in religious services.</p> <p>Also, you may want to remove the vowels symbols from יהוה or the entire text as a whole. Since there were no vowels in old Hebrew, it could help add an older feel to the text.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
